                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/symfony/edit/master/knpu/ep4-services/create-service-class.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>Ready to move a chunk of code <em>out</em> of the controller? Well good for you.</p>
<p>Step 1: create a new PHP class. In <code>AppBundle</code>, I'll create a new directory called
<code>Service</code> - but that could be called <em>anything</em>. Inside, add a new PHP class called
<code>MarkdownTransformer</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="95eb06ced4">
