<p>If you're keeping score at home, that could <em>also</em> be called anything.</p>
<p>Start this with one public function <code>parse()</code> with a <code>$str</code> argument:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="58b705cfbc">
    <div class="meta">
